      "text": "ないわよ\n少なくともLizNoirを続けている間はね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all.\nAt least not while LizNoir is still around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "私の目標はLizNoirがアイドルの頂点に立つこと\n今はそれ以外のことに興味ないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My goal is to stand at the top of the idol world with LizNoir.\nI’m not interested in anything else.",
