      "text": "でも、たまにならこんな仕事もいいかもね\n新鮮な喜びがあったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But a job like this every now and then isn’t so bad.\nIt was a breath of fresh air.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
